{"tid":2252693,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚宵 燒賣一份","createTime":"2020-10-21T15:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T02:02:24.000Z","uid":372785,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9368c62a88f0d4aa8c9f0af0231fda3a49b97a","tid":2252693,"uid":372785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:36:25.000Z","msg":"今晚喺觀塘散步果時<br />\n無啦啦見到間小食店<br />\n於是我就買左十蚊燒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢度十蚊有七粒<br />\n價錢算係咁上下 唔貴又唔平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQOQUWm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQOQUWm.png&h=8f3a0eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講下食評先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢度啲燒賣味度唔錯<br />\n入面冇咩落到麵粉<br />\n唔係一大舊麵包團嚟<br />\n入面有啲魚味<br />\n可能係金龍貨嚟<br />\n<br />\n佢個口感唔錯<br />\n幾煙韌有啲咬口<br />\n不過略有不同嘅係我覺得佢蒸得有少少唔夠淋<br />\n如果蒸耐少少會再好<br />\n<br />\n至於個豉油都ok <br />\n個味道甜甜哋<br />\n我都幾鐘意<br />\n<br />\n整體而言<br />\n啲燒賣幾好食<br />\n下次經過嘅話值得食多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e33e03ccd7cdf08776a9fbbc2843d724d58a810","tid":2252693,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:40:41.000Z","msg":"隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攞嚟打J肯定一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3266f5b77963064e644edb8e1fd61d3de5fc17b2","tid":2252693,"uid":299794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:53:59.000Z","msg":"燒賣師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468313345af97fbff0958999ba655e9f64531192","tid":2252693,"uid":78385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:56:43.000Z","msg":"幾煙韌有啲咬口<br />\n<br />\n咪即係多麵粉囉！"},{"pid":"78b84dfa0b079ff707ddd939b0fae7d04457d3e3","tid":2252693,"uid":372785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e33e03ccd7cdf08776a9fbbc2843d724d58a810","tid":2252693,"